{"id": 582, "genre": 1001, "title": "你受不了哪种说话方式？", "description": "我是如此的挑剔而冷酷，你，不要随便开口。", "record_count": 9699, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183646HsqCFm2vP9OktdSU.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-19T11:26:39Z", "options": [{"id": 18689, "content": "故弄玄虚又不说清楚", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255641}, {"id": 30466, "content": "抖机灵，不说俏皮话会死的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283578}, {"id": 21763, "content": "按你的意思。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281462}, {"id": 19204, "content": "我说我的，他说他的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263404}, {"id": 21508, "content": "别人说他什么都不行。他说别人就行。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254544}, {"id": 23044, "content": "分分钟忘了刚才自己说了什么还要不承认", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288470}, {"id": 24837, "content": "说错还错理直气壮 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304094}, {"id": 30216, "content": "绕弯子 zhuangbility", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334107}, {"id": 21770, "content": "好朋友聊天聊着聊着就开始夸自己，这词还是听了好几遍的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281415}, {"id": 18187, "content": "你知道吗？你知道吗？你知道吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 223, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 111145}, {"id": 18443, "content": "讥笑 不一样 就是讥笑 瞧不起 比如你 哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191092}, {"id": 18188, "content": "还没有等你说完立马就说", "image": null, "praise_count": 752, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257288}, {"id": 18444, "content": "你一个人吗？（还要装作一脸关切地问）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258534}, {"id": 18189, "content": "我还没说话，对方说“就这样了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178865}, {"id": 18445, "content": "后知后觉 说什么都不理你 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259116}, {"id": 18190, "content": "那，你可能就会死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 18191, "content": "感觉自己很卑微然后你很屌", "image": null, "praise_count": 235, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217346}, {"id": 18447, "content": "不看着我眼睛一边做事儿一边和我“说”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232534}, {"id": 18192, "content": "处处压着对方说", "image": null, "praise_count": 1255, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55452}, {"id": 18448, "content": "最讨厌呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228570}, {"id": 18193, "content": "我想怎么怎么样可以吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217346}, {"id": 18449, "content": "不管讨论什么事情 总会忍不住给你来上一堂科普 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207206}, {"id": 18194, "content": "语气词太多，尤其是男的，呀呀呀啦啦啦个不停", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247412}, {"id": 19730, "content": "语言暴力，处处损你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266608}, {"id": 18195, "content": "你就当我没说过啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246814}, {"id": 21267, "content": "总说自己～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269004}, {"id": 18196, "content": "你听我说……", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190076}, {"id": 18452, "content": "自己怎么都对，别人都错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248299}, {"id": 18197, "content": "总给一种自己很伟大的感觉，看点哲理就母爱泛滥", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233797}, {"id": 25621, "content": "特别夸张的关心，看起来好虚伪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 303119}, {"id": 18198, "content": "夹杂各种粗口", "image": null, "praise_count": 577, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}, {"id": 18454, "content": "总是认为自己是对的，总有一万个理由反驳。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164732}, {"id": 18199, "content": "“我不是说你不好，……”结果说的都是不好的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 216, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218555}, {"id": 18455, "content": "人说一句，你蹭十句", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248583}, {"id": 21527, "content": "向别人借橡皮，理直气壮的说:橡皮！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278393}, {"id": 23063, "content": "反问过多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290286}, {"id": 18200, "content": "我要求你……其实是这样的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258093}, {"id": 18456, "content": "自以为懂超多，什么话都敢接", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240966}, {"id": 18968, "content": "我跟你不一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252204}, {"id": 18201, "content": "你明白我的意思吗？ 你明白我要说什么吗？（说这种话的人要么觉得对方是白痴，要么被对方觉得他是白痴）", "image": null, "praise_count": 278, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129211}, {"id": 18202, "content": "完全沉浸在自己的世界，根本不管别人是不是能听明白", "image": null, "praise_count": 179, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224404}, {"id": 18458, "content": "尖叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259233}, {"id": 18203, "content": "芝麻大点事说得比天大……", "image": null, "praise_count": 569, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246346}, {"id": 18459, "content": "打断别人，把所有的话题都往自己身上揽，像别人多想了解你似的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259241}, {"id": 18715, "content": "受不了啰嗦的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215700}, {"id": 18204, "content": "不管别人说什么，上来先说“不是”，然后发表自己的看法，以否定他人表现自己什么都懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1113, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258099}, {"id": 18205, "content": "我是为你好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 186, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162821}, {"id": 18717, "content": "不是的！（提高语调）然后在你反驳之后还是不管逻辑，反正不是的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260491}, {"id": 18206, "content": "恩，哦，呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 428, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256914}, {"id": 18207, "content": "“你先听我说”", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249198}]}